      <title>北京市将补贴国产人工智能芯片 目标到2027年实现自力更生</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/beijing-city-subsidise-domestic-ai-chips-targets-self-reliance-by-2027-2024-04-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着中国寻求发展半导体产业并减少对外国技术的依赖，北京市当局宣布对购买国产人工智能（AI）芯片的企业提供补贴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/beijing-city-subsidise-domestic-ai-chips-targets-self-reliance-by-2027-2024-04-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 01:58:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行维持利率不变，亚洲股市上涨，日元下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行（BOJ）在为期两天的政策会议结束后维持宽松的货币政策立场，周五交易波动较大，而亚洲股市则上涨。]]></description>
